01:27.254 --> 01:30.090 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAT MCCRORY (R), North Carolina:
I firmly
believe that we cannot tolerate
any types

01:30.123 --> 01:31.992 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
