01:32.025 --> 01:37.064 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Appeals for calm
came from
all quarters, from Governor Pat
McCrory on

01:37.097 --> 01:38.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
