02:01.355 --> 02:02.322 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAN: Shots fired.

02:02.356 --> 02:04.157 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Shots fired.

02:04.191 --> 02:07.961 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: A black protester
was critically
wounded, and many in the crowd
accused the

02:07.995 --> 02:09.796 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
