02:09.830 --> 02:13.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: When they shot the guy --
they started
screaming no justice no peace,
and then they

02:13.433 --> 02:15.102 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
