02:34.621 --> 02:35.822 align:left position:25%,start line:73.33% size:75%
KERR PUTNEY,
Charlotte-Mecklenburg, North
Carolina, Police Chief: The
allegation was

02:35.856 --> 02:37.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
