might have been
involved.

02:37.524 --> 02:39.960 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As I said before, guys, we are
here to seek
the truth.

02:39.993 --> 02:44.231 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we're investigating that to
find the truth,
the absolute truth.

02:44.264 --> 02:49.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The city also
faced growing
pressure to release video of the
fatal shooting

02:49.536 --> 02:52.272 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that set the protests in motion.

02:52.305 --> 02:56.777 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
