video raises more
questions.

03:03.116 --> 03:15.195 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KERR PUTNEY: The video doesn't
give me absolute,
definitive visual evidence that
-- that would

03:15.228 --> 03:18.999 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
