that I reviewed.

03:21.435 --> 03:26.373 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The chief said
he's trying
to arrange to let the family see
the video,

03:26.406 --> 03:29.876 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
but he cited state law as a
reason not to
make it public.

03:29.910 --> 03:34.714 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As the day went on, the local
district attorney
asked the state bureau of
investigation to

03:34.748 --> 03:40.053 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
take over the case, while, in
Washington,
Attorney General Loretta Lynch
announced she's

03:40.087 --> 03:44.825 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
