peacekeeping experts,
and she made an appeal of her
own.

03:44.858 --> 03:48.061 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LORETTA LYNCH, U.S. Attorney
General: I urge
those responsible fore bring
violence to these

03:48.095 --> 03:53.767 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
demonstrations to stop, because
you are drowning
out the voices of commitment and
change and

03:53.800 --> 03:56.169 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
you're ushering more tragedy and
grief in
our communities.

03:56.203 --> 04:00.574 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Back in
Charlotte, some of
the city's biggest employers,
from Bank of

04:00.607 --> 04:06.046 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
