Energy, told
workers to stay home.

04:06.079 --> 04:11.384 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Meanwhile, National Guard troops
fanned out,
with hundreds more officers also
expected

04:11.418 --> 04:13.320 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on the streets tonight.

04:13.353 --> 04:18.325 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For some further insight into
what local officials
are doing this evening, I'm
joined by Trevor

04:18.358 --> 04:19.860 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Fuller.

04:19.893 --> 04:22.629 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
