done in the
shooting of this man who they
say didn't deserve

07:44.197 --> 07:45.899 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to be shot to death?

07:45.932 --> 07:51.371 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TREVOR FULLER: Yes, there is no
question that
I grieve for the family of Mr.
Scott.

07:51.404 --> 07:57.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I grieve for the people who are
in the streets
who are protesting.

07:57.844 --> 08:03.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what I believe they are
protesting is
a sense of helplessness, a sense
of feeling

08:03.283 --> 08:07.787 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
under siege, that the system
doesn't seem
to respond to them.

08:07.821 --> 08:13.827 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And so that's why, in
Mecklenburg County,
I have been talking so much
about the challenge

08:13.860 --> 08:15.528 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of economic opportunity.

08:15.562 --> 08:20.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How can we make sure that
prosperity that's
in this county gets shared by
all?

08:20.567 --> 08:27.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have talked about universal
pre-K in Mecklenburg
County, the strength of our
educational system.

08:27.240 --> 08:35.382 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So there is no question that the
protests,
the unrest that we're seeing has
a source,

08:35.415 --> 08:37.183 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a legitimate source.

08:37.217 --> 08:43.656 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Our challenge now is, how do we
get to the
root of that and solve it
without violence?

08:43.690 --> 08:46.025 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And what do you
think the answer
to that is?

08:46.059 --> 08:50.730 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TREVOR FULLER: Well, the answer
is, first,
we have to regain calm.

08:50.764 --> 08:56.636 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have to regain security,
because, my view
is, when emotions are high,
intelligence is

08:56.669 --> 08:58.471 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
low.

08:58.505 --> 09:04.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so we have got to get our
community in
a place of safety, so that we
can have these

09:04.210 --> 09:11.684 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
conversations that we need to
have, conversations
about who shares an economic
prosperity, conversations,

09:11.718 --> 09:14.087 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
difficult conversations about
race.

09:14.120 --> 09:17.757 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But it's very difficult to have
those conversations
when people do not feel safe.

09:17.791 --> 09:20.660 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And so we first have to
establish safety.

09:20.693 --> 09:25.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then we need to not only
have the dialogue,
but also have a plan of action
and execute

09:25.698 --> 09:27.634 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on it.

09:27.667 --> 09:32.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Trevor Fuller,
who is the Mecklenburg
County commission chair, we
thank you very

09:32.705 --> 09:33.673 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

09:33.706 --> 09:35.675 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TREVOR FULLER: Thank you very
much, Judy.

09:35.708 --> 09:40.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: In the day's other
news: Prosecutors
in Tulsa, Oklahoma, charged a
white policewoman

09:40.814 --> 09:44.350 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
