executive director of the racial
justice organization

16:41.234 --> 16:46.272 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Color of Change, Vanessa De
Luca, editor in
chief of "Essence,"a magazine
for and about

16:46.305 --> 16:51.244 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
