rejoicing, lots of excitement
about that,

17:05.591 --> 17:10.963 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
upbeat, and, at the same time,
the same conversations
turn to what's happening in
Charlotte, what's

17:10.997 --> 17:12.164 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
happening in Tulsa.

17:12.198 --> 17:14.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Rashad Robinson, there is a
dichotomy at work
here.

17:14.433 --> 17:16.269 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
