17:16.302 --> 17:18.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RASHAD ROBINSON, Executive
Director, Color
of Change: I think there
absolutely is a dichotomy.

17:18.638 --> 17:24.944 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it speaks to this idea of
that not mistaking
presence for power, that just
because we are

17:24.977 --> 17:30.049 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
