ahead and then
steps backwards.

17:35.087 --> 17:40.893 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And while we see huge steps
forward -- I got
to see a sneak peek of that
museum last night,

17:40.927 --> 17:42.895 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
