20:11.677 --> 20:15.714 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I would never quibble with
anyone if someone
said desegregation did me no
favors.

20:15.748 --> 20:19.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Well, except that,
