famous were the
persuaders themselves, who make
a living beckoning

46:22.513 --> 46:24.348 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
us every step we take.

46:24.382 --> 46:29.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT CIALDINI: Those ads,
