46:55.613 --> 46:57.448 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Before they even
hear it even.

46:57.481 --> 47:03.254 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT CIALDINI: It is what you
say immediately
before you deliver your message
that leverages

47:03.287 --> 47:04.689 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
